(7, 'Privacy Policy', 'প্রাইভেসি পলিসি', 'privacy-policy', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \"Arial Nova\", sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Geo Assure values your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes\r\nhow we (“Geo Assure” or “Robi” or “Pragati Life Insurance” or “the web” or “the\r\nproduct” or its developer “E. B. Solutions Ltd.” or its sister concern “E. B.\r\nSolutions Ltd.” or “EBS”) handle user data (e.g., information provided by a\r\nuser, collected about a user.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\n\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\">How Geo\r\nAssure Handles User Data</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\"><br>\r\n<strong>Information you provide: </strong>We may collect and\r\nstore any information you provide through our web or other related services.\r\nThat is Geo Assure only collects the data provided by only you while sign up\r\n(your name, date of birth, phone number) <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\n\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\">Use Of\r\n“Cookies” To Collect Information</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\"><br>\r\nCookies are small data files that a website you visit may save on your computer\r\nor handheld device that usually includes an anonymous unique identifier. Our\r\nwebsites and those of our Products may use cookies for user authentication,\r\nkeeping track of your preferences, promotional campaigns, tracking our audience\r\nsize and traffic patterns, and in certain other cases. We may include small\r\ngraphic images in our email messages and newsletters to determine whether the\r\nmessages were opened and the links were viewed.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\"><br>\r\nThird-party advertisers may also create and access cookies, which will be\r\nsubject to their privacy policies – we accept no responsibility or liability\r\nfor the use of such third parties’ cookies. If you do not wish cookies to be\r\nplaced on your PC or handheld device, then they can be disabled in your web\r\nbrowser. The option to do so is normally found in your browser’s “security\r\nsettings” section. Please note that permanently disabling cookies in your\r\nbrowser may hinder your use of our websites as well as other websites and\r\ninteractive services.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\n\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\">Security</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\"><br>\r\n <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\">All security on our websites is\r\ntreated seriously. Where applicable, we undertake security steps, including use\r\nof SSL technology, on our back-end systems that store customer account\r\ninformation and to protect data transmissions. However, this is not a guarantee\r\nthat such data transmissions cannot be accessed, altered or deleted due to\r\nfirewall or other security software failures.<br>\r\n <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\">If you have any further\r\nconcerns about security, please email our Customer Support Team at </span><span style=\"color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\"><a href=\"mailto:info@ebsbd.com\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial\"> info@ebsbd.com</span></a></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";\r\ncolor:#333333\"> or write to the following address:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\n\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\">E. B.\r\nSolutions Pte. Ltd.</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\n\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\"><br>\r\nHouse No: 32 (7th floor), Road No. 02<br>\r\nDhanmondi, Dhaka 1205,<br>\r\nBangladesh<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\"> </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\"> </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\n\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\">Disclosure\r\nof User Data</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\"><br>\r\nGeo Assure collects Personal Information and other information from you in\r\norder to but are not limited to:<br>\r\n-Support user authentication/security and content recommendation;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\">-Determine your current\r\ngeographic location/language for localized content/services;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\">-Comply with the requirements\r\nof our partners;<br>\r\n-Notify you of changes to this Privacy Policy and other policies;<br>\r\n-Integrate with additional service providers for use of the Services;<br>\r\n-Personalize our Services to better reflect particular interests and\r\npreferences; and<br>\r\n-Generally improve your experience. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\">Additionally, we may use\r\nanonymous Personal Information and share it in an aggregated form with third\r\nparties, advertisers and/or business partners in order to analyze Service\r\nusage, improve the Services and your experience, or for other similar purposes.\r\nSuch (anonymous) use of information is not subject to any restrictions under\r\nthis Privacy Policy.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\"><br>\r\nFurthermore, should you breach our terms and conditions or terms of use or if\r\nwe are under a duty to disclose or share your personal data in order to comply\r\nwith any legal obligation, we may disclose your information to a relevant\r\nauthority. This may include exchanging information with other companies and\r\norganizations for the purposes of fraud protection and credit risk reduction.\r\nAny disclosure of personal information will be strictly controlled and made\r\nfully in accordance with current international law or the law of the area of\r\nthe concerned case of business.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\r\n\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\">Data\r\nDeletion Policy</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\ncolor:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">As part of our continuing dedication to data\r\nsecurity and customer privacy, Geo Assure offers all users the opportunity to\r\nrequest data deletion for any data associated with their account. But note that\r\nif you want to proceed with data deletion request you have to deregister the\r\nservice or insurance policies in which you are subscribed. Geo Assure only\r\ncollects the information that is related to your subscribed policy(-ies), due\r\nto which it will hinder the process of premium and claim process if you want to\r\ndelete data without deregistering. You have to sign up again if you want to\r\nobtain service through our website. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:\"Open Sans\";color:black;mso-themecolor:text1\">To place </span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\"Arial Nova\",sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n\"Open Sans\";color:#333333\">a data deletion request please send us the details\r\nat info@ebsbd.com in the following format.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: i