\" new=\"\" roman\",serif\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 20px;\">Maternity:</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 20px;\">&nbsp;Hospitalization due to any maternity related issue will not be covered<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"ColorfulList-Accent11CxSpMiddle\" style=\"line-height: 19.5px; margin-left: 31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 20px;\">Eligibility:</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 20px;\">&nbsp;Only continuous enrolled subscriber will be eligible for life insurance coverage benefit. No benefit shall be paid under life insurance coverage for all preexisting disease, Suicide,&nbsp;(AIDS) or any AIDS related illness, attempted commission of an assault or any unlawful act, or being engaged in any illegal activity or felony.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"ColorfulList-Accent11CxSpMiddle\" style=\"line-height: 19.5px; margin-left: 31.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 20px;\">Natural Death Benefit (NDB):</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 20px;\">&nbsp;In case of death of an Insured Member due to any reason (except death due to AIDS and HIV related disease any time and suicide) the sum assured amount will be paid as per policy legal nominee of the respective deceased member.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"ColorfulList-Accent11CxSpMiddle\" style=\"line-height: 19.5px; margin-left: 31.5pt; text-indent: -4.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 20px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<a name=\"_Hlk93412168\">Accidental Death Benefit (ADB):</a></span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;=\"\" mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 20px;\">&nbsp;If an Insured Member dies directly from an accident caused through external and fierce means (except death due to any unlawful activities) the sum assured amount will be paid as per policy legal nominee of the respective deceased member. No ADB benefit is payable in such cases.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"ColorfulList-Accent11CxSpLast\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin-left: 31.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">General Exclusions &amp; Special Conditions</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",serif;mso-bidi-font-weight:=\"\" bold\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt 40.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -9pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Costs we don’t cover</span></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 31.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">There are some costs that your policy does not cover.&nbsp; We will not pay any expenses arising from, caused by or in connection with:</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 31.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0in; font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Medical Expenses incurred for any disease / illness within 30 days</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;of the commencement of the Policy Period. Accidents would be covered from Day 1.</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 31.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"text-indent: 0in; text-align: left; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0in; text-align: left; font-weight: bolder;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Acts of terrorism, war and illegal acts.</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 31.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0in; font-weight: bolder;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Treatment&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt;\">of any illness or injury resulting directly or indirectly from, or as a consequence of, any act of terrorism, war&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt;\">(whether declared or not) act of foreign invasion or hostility, civil war, riot, rebellion, revolution, insurrection or any active involvement in any similar event (unless you are an innocent bystander) or injury sustained whilst involved in any illegal act.</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 31.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"text-indent: 0in; text-align: left; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0in; text-align: left; font-weight: bolder;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Alcohol or drug abuse</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 31.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Treatment</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;of alcoholism or drug abuse or any condition cause by the over use of alcohol or the misuse of drugs prescribed or otherwise.</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 31.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0in; font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Alternative therapies</span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 49.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Alternative treatment or therapies of any kind including homeopathy, naturopathy, reflexology, acupuncture, bone setting, hydrotherapy, herbalist treatment, hypnotism, massage therapy, aromatherapy, or any treatment other than allopathic western medicine</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 49.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; font-family: Wingdings;\">Ø<span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: 0in; font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"font-size: 